{"tid":1673668,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【美參議員Ted Cruz專訪】美國公司為打入中國 不惜摒棄做人價值觀","createTime":"2019-10-24T18:59:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-25T01:21:55.000Z","uid":141151,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"c48bd6672f2503773f6fda246c62379be7890814","tid":1673668,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T18:59:33.000Z","msg":"【美參議員專訪】美國公司為打入中國 不惜摒棄做人價值觀<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/news/%E7%BE%8E%E5%8F%83%E8%AD%B0%E5%93%A1%E5%B0%88%E8%A8%AA%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E5%85%AC%E5%8F%B8%E7%82%BA%E6%89%93%E5%85%A5%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B-%E4%B8%8D%E6%83%9C%E6%91%92%E6%A3%84%E5%81%9A%E4%BA%BA%E5%83%B9%E5%80%BC%E8%A7%80-091808645.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.yahoo.com%2Fnews%2F%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%258F%2583%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E5%2593%25A1%25E5%25B0%2588%25E8%25A8%25AA%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%258F%25B8%25E7%2582%25BA%25E6%2589%2593%25E5%2585%25A5%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B-%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%2583%259C%25E6%2591%2592%25E6%25A3%2584%25E5%2581%259A%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%2583%25B9%25E5%2580%25BC%25E8%25A7%2580-091808645.html&d=wRNUG5%2F8jzvhtT%2FDMFjpNv4N63GW6AE6v5vQ0jPanwo%3D&h=0e3b8c80\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/news/%E7%BE%8E%E5%8F%83%E8%AD%B0%E5%93%A1%E5%B0%88%E8%A8%AA%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E5%85%AC%E5%8F%B8%E7%82%BA%E6%89%93%E5%85%A5%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B-%E4%B8%8D%E6%83%9C%E6%91%92%E6%A3%84%E5%81%9A%E4%BA%BA%E5%83%B9%E5%80%BC%E8%A7%80-091808645.html</a><br />\n<br />\n美國參議員Ted Cruz在周三表示，中國是「美國面臨最大的長期地緣政治威脅」，因為高風險的貿易戰與其他觸發點融合，加劇了全球兩大經濟體系之間的緊張局勢。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">這個得克薩斯州共和黨議員和2016年共和黨總統候選人，日前接受Yahoo財經總編輯Andy Serwer訪問，描述了他在日本、台灣、印度和香港的亞洲之旅。<br />\n<br />\n他解釋說，這次到訪中國的鄰近地區，目的是和「朋友和盟國」見面，重點是探討如何「應對中國不斷增強的軍事侵略」。<br />\n<br />\nCruz對Yahoo財經說：「您知道，中國正將軍隊現代化，這很大程度上是靠從美國盜取技術和知識產權做到，他們將盜取知識產權作為政策議程。那威脅是真實存在的。」</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n這個得克薩斯州的參議員繼續抨擊中國的人權記錄，稱其「糟糕透頂」，指出被關押在「再教育營」中遭受酷刑甚至死亡的穆斯林維吾爾人數多達100萬人。而在香港的抗爭運動中，美國一些大型跨國公司中了圈套，Cruz說它們著重盈利多於基本的價值觀。<br />\n<br />\nCruz說：「[我]一直反對中國侵犯人權。」<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">「現在我們看到更危險的是，很多美國公司迫切地希望在中國賺錢 - 我明白到進入中國可以令他們賺很多的錢 - 但是我們的基本價值觀，例如言論自由，是不能出賣的，」他補充說。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n據報，蘋果公司香港手機刪除了台灣旗的 emoji ，並將兩個香港抗爭者使用的應用程式下架。<br />\n<br />\n「我不認為美國公司應協助或教唆共產主義政府進行壓迫和審查，」Cruz補充說。<br />\n<br />\n撰文：Julia La Roche"},{"pid":"c060500e3a61c64ebd4c13e09980c2a7473d0dde","tid":1673668,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T19:00:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/guewjRY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FguewjRY.jpg&h=ac95176a&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"fb56c09d9a6cf7070a4ad3ce7481b5dc159f7e7d","tid":1673668,"uid":130695,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T19:01:49.000Z","msg":"入到中国咪又係人血饅頭<br />\n十鳩億人傳銷咁被捐錢<br />\nN咁多種稅交到傻閪<br />\n平均13個中国人養1個中国黨員"},{"pid":"78ab9701028972a19778d77c0099538fbb8962a7","tid":1673668,"uid":197640,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T19:23:23.000Z","msg":"蘋果呢次實比美國國會查<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67390ecf3c7a5f98dcd32850680c0197a7804719","tid":1673668,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T19:25:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d453c3c8fd804dd58749dbda0442c949697405bb","tid":1673668,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T19:27:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c44eeeeeadc583a632605e858ed3b9787edca